{"tid":2000963,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［文革］藍絲組織開始搞通識科","createTime":"2020-05-04T07:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T19:19:23.000Z","uid":6132,"like":36,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"5e28036066df8d252785a5ec8e98aea4418b518e","tid":2000963,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:54:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vRMuGdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvRMuGdp.jpg&h=dec5db5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有藍絲指控元朗趙中通識科教材偏頗<br />\n<br />\n呢啲係佢哋嘅截圖，你會發現啲資料通常係到資料三就冇咗，又或者冇咗幾個資料<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Vn9Gdp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Vn9Gdp.jpg&h=f5944b03&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnu0NTq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fpnu0NTq.jpg&h=1070daec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rzrFNTq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrzrFNTq.jpg&h=e7afa332&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BoPj3rL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBoPj3rL.jpg&h=71491995&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MR2d7Tr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMR2d7Tr.jpg&h=99d0e3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nRbB5E6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnRbB5E6.jpg&h=681eeb3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KMMOcj6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKMMOcj6.jpg&h=fadd3c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gBbB5E7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgBbB5E7.jpg&h=bee5b238&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXUHgMN.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXUHgMN.jpg&h=7d1b839e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xniABMQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxniABMQ.jpg&h=f6be9f66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2vCP6R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2vCP6R.jpg&h=cf58de9c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n利申舊生，以我所知呢啲資料係唔同來源，立場有正有反，一個議題通常有6-8個資料，同學就議題睇完咁多份資料之後，就分組討論正反論點<br />\n<br />\n而公民抗命、西環治港，呢啲概念亦都係常常接觸到嘅字眼，冇可能唔教<br />\n而呢啲概念完全符合通識科課程指引<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZiPj3yc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZiPj3yc.png&h=5bd9022b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而下面都有留言話個藍絲淨cut一邊立場嘅資料，以偏概全<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6pzSkc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6pzSkc.jpg&h=a290a228&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nLink在此，入去屌柒啲藍絲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=228221935273760&amp;id=100144411414847&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D228221935273760%26id%3D100144411414847%26__tn__%3D%252As%252As-R&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=7f35c394\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=228221935273760&amp;id=100144411414847&amp;__tn__=%2As%2As-R</a>"},{"pid":"794e1b28bb2d7fda8fa238f7fce77bf1620b086d","tid":2000963,"uid":6132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-04T07:56:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/100144411414847/posts/228221935273760/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F100144411414847%2Fposts%2F228221935273760%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=LQBsT8b49a%2FdXTDbQfnWX%2BQdxvW7LhoH5lY2nOShEJQ%3D&h=73c58f9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/10014441